{"type":"message","id":"c191007a","parentId":"fd373fed","timestamp":"2026-04-02T17:48:03.285Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-04-03 01:48 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态（企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务），整理3-5条关键信息，写入 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}],"timestamp":1775152083282}}
