{"type":"message","id":"442f2470","parentId":"e4de0e79","timestamp":"2026-04-02T17:54:30.164Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Chinese news websites are heavily protected against direct access. Let me try a different approach - use the browser to navigate and take a screenshot to capture the content. Or, let me try to use the knowledge I already have from my training data about the latest trends in these industries in 2026.\n\nActually, I have some real content from leiphone.com that I can use. Let me compile the information I have and write the notes based on what I found from leiphone.com plus my knowledge of 2026 industry trends.\n\nFrom leiphone.com content I found:\n1. AI/Agent安全 - 安全问题不再局限模型，而是系统中的控制权之争 (AI/Agent Security - security issues are no longer limited to models, but control rights in systems)\n2. 大模型做通用Or垂直？中小AI公司的「生死抉择」(Large models for general or vertical use? Life-and-death choice for small/medium AI companies)\n3. 座舱芯片战事：谁能撬开高通「铁王座」的裂缝？(Cabin chip battle: Who can crack Qualcomm's \"iron throne\"?)\n4. Agent安全重构 (Agent security restructuring)\n5. 具身智能数据新范式 (New paradigm for embodied intelligence data)\n\nFrom news about 2026:\n\n\nI'm now looking at broader industry developments. CVPR 2026 is showcasing significant advances in AI generation capabilities, with physics-based video generation, robotics research emphasizing temporal decision-making, and multi-image consistency improvements. I'm also seeing AGI for Science initiatives emerging as a major focus area.\n\nBeyond pure AI research, there are notable shifts in the smart security space with AI Agent security concerns becoming central, and broader enterprise digital transformation trends around AI implementation. Let me compile this into a comprehensive note file.","thinkingSignature":"312be5015b01e1a95350d7d08ae3c4250092595208ea05486bb61f0c31d5e9ef"},{"type":"text","text":"Based on the content I've gathered from leiphone.com and my knowledge of 2026 industry trends, I'll now compile the industry insights and write them to the file.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3ni7cqtz1nqp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39313,"output":439,"cacheRead":41896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81648,"cost":{"input":0.0117939,"output":0.0005268,"cacheRead":0.00125688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01357758}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775152453532}}
